COMMENT ON COLUMN beneficial_owners.address_encrypted IS 'Encrypted home address (PII, FieldLevelEncryption).';
COMMENT ON COLUMN beneficial_owners.ownership_percentage IS 'Percent of the Business owned by this individual (0-100).';
COMMENT ON COLUMN beneficial_owners.is_control_person IS 'True when this individual is the designated control person per CDD (one is required when no owner crosses 25%).';

