COMMENT ON COLUMN interactions.interaction_type IS 'Note, Call, Visit, Task, Meeting, or SystemEvent.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN interactions.subject IS 'Short subject line (used in compound PK).';
COMMENT ON COLUMN interactions.body IS 'Long-form body of the interaction.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN interactions.interaction_date IS 'Date the interaction occurred or was logged.';
